It would be great to have a 'notify me in X days' option when creating, commenting or resolving an issue, to remind the user to do something about it after a certain period of time.  This could be made periodic, terminating on some event (typically 'issue closed').

{panel:bgColor=#e7f4fa}
  *NOTE:* This suggestion is for *JIRA Cloud*. Using *JIRA Server*? [See the corresponding suggestion|http://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JRASERVER-2841].
